Comment.val: /*Service will return all the instruments coupled to the given list of calculation rules ordered by Id. Paging possible. Also the total number of linked instruments can be determined. XSD's : - nl.topicus.epp.scf.getinstrumentsforcalcrules.request.xsd - nl.topicus.epp.scf.getinstrumentsforcalcrules.response.xsd */

Text.val: One Extra record to be able to determine if the next record is present:

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT COUNT(*) "TOTALNUMBER" FROM ( SELECT DISTINCT b.be_volgnummer FROM security_tax_tariff s INNER JOIN tax_tarif t ON t.tt_id = s.sctt_tt_id INNER JOIN beleggingsinstrument b ON b.be_volgnummer = s.sctt_be_id WHERE t.tt_cfcu_id IN (:1) )

select * from (select distinct b.be_volgnummer, b.be_symbool,b.be_optietype, b.be_expiratiedatum,b.be_exerciseprijs from security_tax_tariff s inner join tax_tarif t on t.tt_id = s.sctt_tt_id inner join beleggingsinstrument b on b.be_volgnummer = s.sctt_be_id where b.be_volgnummer >= ~1 and t.tt_cfcu_id in (:2) order by b.be_volgnummer) :3
